createTables: DROP TABLE IF EXISTS Items; CREATE TABLE Items ('barcode' INTEGER, 'bar_type' TEXT, 'scan_agent' TEXT, 'scan_location' TEXT, 'scan_date' NUMERIC, 'scan_time' NUMERIC)
insertItems: INSERT OR IGNORE INTO Items (barcode, bar_type, scan_agent, scan_location, scan_date, scan_time) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
